'''"Piracy is theft"''' was a propaganda slogan used by UK non-profit organization [[Federation Against Software Theft|FAST]] (Federation Against Software Theft).<ref>http://www.ntk.net/2002/11/29/elspa.gif</ref><ref>http://worldofstuart.excellentcontent.com/antipiracy.htm</ref> It was first used in the 1980s and has since then been used by other similar organisations such as [[Motion Picture Association of America|MPAA]].<ref>[http://news.zdnet.com/2100-9595_22-520722.html Inside the online movie underground]</ref>
